QuestData.Title: Private Chat
QuestData.Description: Look... one last favor before you run off.$B$BPrivate Worcester is still back at that tower "recruiting." Go and let him know that we're good to pack it up now. Back to town.$B$BPleasure working with you, recruit.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Private Worcester at the Orgrimmar Rocketway Exchange.
QuestData.RewardText: What?! I got left out of the action completely? Are you serious?$B$BAlright, alright... no shooting the messenger. Thanks for the news, bud. Maybe I'll see you back at town.
